scsi: mpi3mr: Additional event handling

Implement support for handling the following MPI events:

 - MPI3_EVENT_SAS_BROADCAST_PRIMITIVE
 - MPI3_EVENT_CABLE_MGMT
 - MPI3_EVENT_ENERGY_PACK_CHANGE

